    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I feel like there is much more to lodash than just map, filter and each. It helps write complex code in a few lines, with method names that are explicit and clearly tell what the intent is. It's not just a polyfill, it really helps you write better code and focus on the business logic.\n\nFor me the improved readability and maintenance is worth the extra size. Of course, this is true only if we can select which part of lodash to import and not import blindly the whole lib.\n",
