    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I remember a few PRs with comments like \"Ooh, nice easy lodash one-liner\". I just feel like if we are going to code ourselves the same helpers that what lodash is already doing, then we should just use the damn library :)\n\nBut yes, this is subjective, I personnally am more productive with lodash than without.\n",
