    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We use it for now, we only need to be careful at only using it when absolutely necessary, not for bind/map etc.. And always think about the underlying data structure: can we make it/refactor so that the number of calls to lodash (or even regular map etc..) is not so needed?\n",
